    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "四朝臣",
        "大太监",
        "秦二世",
        "赵女",
        "赵高"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。四小太监、二大太监、秦二世同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦二世",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "凤阁龙楼，万古千秋。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四朝臣同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四朝臣",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣等见驾，吾皇万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦二世",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众卿平身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四朝臣",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵高上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣赵高见驾，吾皇万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦二世",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "平身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦二世",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "卿女可曾带上金殿？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣启万岁，臣女昨晚偶得疯症，请主定夺。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦二世",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "昨晚灯光之下还是好人，怎么得了疯症？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有道是：天有不测风云，人有旦夕祸福。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦二世",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赐她龙车凤辇，带上金殿，寡人观看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵高下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦二世",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "御林军走上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "御林军走上哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四御林军同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "殿角伺候。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵高、哑丫鬟、赵女同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "低着头下了这龙车凤辇，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "行一步来至在玉石阶前。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（哑丫鬟示意在殿外等候，赵女点头，哑丫鬟下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "到如今顾不得抛头露面。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿啊，随我上殿。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵女冷笑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，坏了，坏了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "看看这无道君怎把旨传。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿啊，上面就是万岁，上前见驾。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我晓得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哟，上面坐的敢莫是皇帝老官，恭喜你万福，贺喜你发财呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦二世",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗯！见了寡人因何不跪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有道是，你大人不下位，我生员么，喏喏喏，是不跪的哟！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦二世",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "果然疯癫，倒叫寡人好笑哇！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦二世",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我也好笑哇！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦二世",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗯！寡人笑你疯癫，你笑寡人何来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你笑得我疯癫，我就笑得你荒淫无道！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦二世",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎见得寡人无道？"
        },
        {
          "character": "四朝臣",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾主乃有道明君。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "列位大人，老哥，你等听了！想先皇当年，东巡岱海，西建阿房，南修五岭，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "北造万里长城；指望江山万代，永保平安，谁知你这昏王贪恋酒色，不理朝纲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我想这天下乃人人之天下，非你一人之天下，似你这等荒淫无道，我看这江"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "山，你家未必坐得长久哟！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "这昏王失仁义民心大变，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听谗言害忠良败坏江山。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦二世",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "真乃疯话，哪里容得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦二世",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "左右，刀门架起！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唗！我乃玉皇之女，法力无边，岂容你等大胆，放肆！还不与我退正点了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "怒气儿我把这云鬟扯乱，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "将这些众狂徒就斩首在马前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "只气得牙关儿咬破舌尖"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我手中有兵刃决一死战"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦二世",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再若疯癫，斫头来见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀呀，我也不知你这皇帝老官有多大前程，动不动就要斫头来见。我且问你，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一个人的头斫了下来，还长得上么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "长不上了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么讲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "长不上了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "哭头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊……老爹爹，我的儿啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，又来了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "这一番在金殿装疯弄险，"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦二世",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赶下殿去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（哑丫鬟迎上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "但不知何日里夫妻重圆。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（三笑） 哈哈，哈哈，啊哈哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（哑丫鬟扶赵女同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老臣领罪。"
        },
        {
